&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a specialist Plain film radiographer to broaden their experience within the community hospital sites, including Redcar Primary Care hospital Urgent care centre, East Cleveland, Guisborough and One Life sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The services within the community sites are varied and host a wide range of clinics including those held by consultants from the acute sector. There will be an expectation to work any hours within a 24/7 day service with the possibly of some rotation/cross cover at any of the South Tees NHS trust radiology sites .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic people to join our team where our purpose is to deliver seamless, high quality, safe healthcare for all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;South Tees Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust is already nationally recognised as one of the leading healthcare providers in England for the quality of our services. The Trust has a designated regional major trauma centre with a 24-hour acute admissions unit and specialised services in cancer, neurosciences, spinal injuries, cardiology and renal medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
